claim: Jackie Evancho has released three songs that made Billboard 200 top 10 debuts.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Jacqueline Marie `` Jackie '' Evancho  (  -LSB- iːˈvæŋkoʊ -RSB- ; born April 9 , 2000  )  is an American classical crossover singer who gained wide recognition at an early age and , since 2009 , has issued an EP and seven albums , including a platinum and gold album and three Billboard 200 top 10 debuts .
